data.description: Discover your dream home with breathtaking views! This expansive 3-bedroom residence, complete with a bonus retreat room and above ground pool, offers the perfect blend of space, comfort, and natural beauty. Nestled on a generous 1.19-acre horse property on the hillside and no HOA, it provides a picturesque panorama of Cottonwood city below and boasts the incredible advantage of being just steps away from the serene national forest. With room to spare, this home invites you to create your ideal lifestyle while maintaining proximity to all the amenities of town life. What's more, its construction on a sturdy 2x6 stem wall ensures that financing options like FHA and VA are readily available, making it easier than ever to turn your homeownership dreams into a reality. Embrace the tranquility of hillside living while staying connected to the heart of Cottonwood - your perfect home awaits!
